name: Steven Eric
description: I am a Honest man looking for honest woman to honor and respect. I don’t lie or cheat and I am looking for the same in a woman. A woman who believes age is just a number, who knows what loves is and what it takes to be in love. someone who will love me for who i am and my kid as hers and i will love hers kids too as i love my daughter. Someone who is looking for something serious because i am looking for the woman i will spend the rest of my life with.
